title: Did Ivanka celebrate the news media showing Trump's victory in Alaska?
subtitle: Some have called Trump's eldest daughter to celebrate Alaska's call while ignoring the same director calling the election generally to Joe Biden.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The daughter of President Donald Trump and the White House adviser, Ivanka Trump, celebrated her father ' s invitation to Associated Press Laska in the 2020 elections, after asking the President why the media were making such contacts while the general elections were not in his favor.
